## SfChart

### Bug fixes
{:#sfchart-bug-fixes}

* \#166730 - Now [`TooltipTemplate`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.ChartSeries~TooltipTemplate.html) is working properly for [`PieSeries`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.PieSeries.html) in iOS.

* \#166846 - [`EdgeLabelsVisibilityMode`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.RangeAxisBase~EdgeLabelsVisibilityMode.html) is working properly when [`Minimum`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.NumericalAxis~Minimum.html) and [`Maximum`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.NumericalAxis~Maximum.html) properties are set in iOS.

* \#166848 - Now data markers will be visible for all data points in 100% stacked series.

* \#165513 - "Unable to access disposed object" exception will no longer be thrown in any scenarios in Android.

* \#166303 - Now [`SelectedDataPointIndex`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.ChartSeries~SelectedDataPointIndex.html) property will work in two-way binding mode.

* \#165422 - Issue with improper positioning of [`Tooltip`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.ChartTooltipBehavior.html) when [`AutoScrolling`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.ChartAxis~AutoScrollingDelta.html) feature is enabled has been fixed.

* \#165198 - Memory leak in [`Trackball`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.ChartTrackballBehavior.html) label with DataTemplate has been fixed.

* \#165422 - [`DataMarker`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.ChartDataMarker_members.html) label template will work properly while zooming and panning in Android.

* \#164221 - Memory leak  will no longer occur in [`Legend`](https://help.syncfusion.com/xamarin/sfchart/legend) while navigating between pages in UWP.

* \#165687 - [`SfChart`](https://help.syncfusion.com/xamarin/sfchart/getting-started) will scroll properly while placing chart inside the scroll viewer in UWP.

### Enhancement
{:#sfchart-enhancement}

* \#160777 - Now you can place the [`ChartAxis`](https://help.syncfusion.com/cr/cref_files/xamarin/sfchart/Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms~Syncfusion.SfChart.XForms.ChartAxis.html) labels in multiple lines using \n.